snippet.title: Jeff Favignano
snippet.description:
What's up everyone? Thanks for checking out my channel! First and foremost I am just a human being like you that enjoys playing video games and guitar with friends. I recently moved to Tampa FL and I love it here! Thanks to all of the support from my subscribers I am now a full-time YouTuber!
Subscribe if you like what you see, I upload often.
